3415.Name: Greater Hartford Men's PTI 25+
3415.Details:
Entry: $180 per team
	Please contact tournament Director for details.

Note: The eligibility for this event is based on the team being a combined 25 PTI or over (vs most PTI tournaments where the eligibility is based on both players being above the stated 25+ threshold)

 	All players must be current APTA members or pay a $30 Limited Membership Fee, good for one tournament. Join the APTA
 	All matches best of 3 tie break sets.

Three matches guaranteed (weather permitting)
 	Official APTA rules will govern play
 	 No Jeans PolicyPlease respect HGC “no jeans” dress code.

TO REGISTER CLICK ON REGISTER LINK ABOVE
